==English==

{{rank|standing|books|knows|622|try|loved|deal|distance}}

===Pronunciation===
*trī, /traɪ/, /traI/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aɪ|Rhymes: -aɪ]]

===Verb===
'''to try''' ([[tries]], [[tried]], [[trying]])

# to attempt.
#:''I tried to [[rollerblade]], but I couldn’t''.
# to work on something.
#:''Trying too hard.''
# to taste, sample, etc.
#:''Try this—you’ll [[love#Verb|love]] it''.
# to put on trial.
#:''He was tried and [[execute]]d''.
# to tire.
#:''He was trying...''

====Synonyms====
*(1): [[attempt]]
*(2): [[sample]], [[taste]]

